{"tid":1940303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"myradio有人phone in今晚踩場講沙嶺死亡人數的異常","createTime":"2020-03-23T16:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-25T19:17:41.000Z","uid":26770,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44d85dfe40f38fb63e35d20ad0331cff98b6ad46","tid":1940303,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:33:16.000Z","msg":"觀眾phone in自己去過沙嶺公墓,<ins>見到2019-2020沙嶺下葬者大增</ins><br />\n<br />\n我認為就算係自殺墮樓同浮屍家人都會去認屍<br />\n<strong>自私冷血藍屍更會認屍,因為班賤種怕影響家運</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港警魔唔敢通知受害者父母認屍,因為死者身上有遭性侵及私刑的痕跡</span><br />\n陳妹妹母親所以要死係因為當時警魔未有完善棄屍守則,按正常手續把陳妹妹屍體入倉,唯有威迫利誘陳妹妹媽媽簽燒屍"},{"pid":"245d7b106cd423bd110e694c5c082bcd0b03be23","tid":1940303,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e22bf10aed6cbbb423ab2f716f70a4ebc268eb","tid":1940303,"uid":238475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"搵人mark 低 車牌 日期 時間。<br />\n將來都係重要證據的一種!!"},{"pid":"f804d89fa0dcc25f041615c141f7b0f95161d94a","tid":1940303,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:37:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4159c0eb70cde95b1ed79b302a610cfbb419dea","tid":1940303,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-23T16:42:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"